<a href="mailto:silat@infernalseraphs.com">A_Shaman01</a> of the Cazic-Thule server on Oct. 12, 2000 at 10:06am said...<br>
Mobs do not summon pets anymore, so you really don't have to worry about pulling them or looking for them, because they are NOT there.  "Thought Destroyers" drop a bp needed for the new Pally Epic Quest.  If you're a newbie to the zone, don't be afraid to say so.  Silly mistakes get you and others killed, and result in forcing the cleric to a res another person.  Also, never ask when your equipment dropping mob is getting pulled, nothing sucks more than people spamming the puller with tells.<br><br>
